quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  22,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  22,1,logo! apne perwar-digaar se daro. ke qayamat ka zalzala aik hadisaaٴ azeem hoga
  22,2,( ae mukhatib ) jis din to is ko dekhe ga ( uss din yeh haal hoga ke ) tamam doodh pilanay wali aurtain apne bachon ko bhool jayen gi. aur tamam hamal valyon ke hamal gir parrin ge. aur log tujh ko matawaale nazar ayen ge magar woh matawaale nahi hon ge balkay ( azaab dekh kar ) madhosh ho rahay hon ge. be shak khuda ka azaab bara sakht hai
  22,3,aur baaz log aisay hain jo khuda ( ki shaan ) mein ilm ( o dansih ) ke baghair jhagarte aur har shetan sarkash ki pairwi karte hain
  22,4,jis ke baray mein likh diya gaya hai ke jo usay dost rakhay ga to is ko gumraah kardey ga aur dozakh ke azaab ka rasta dukhaay ga
  22,5,logo agar tum ko marnay ke baad jee utney mein kuch shak ho to hum ne tum ko ( pehli baar bhi to ) pedakiya tha ( yani ibtida mein ) matti se phir is se nutfa bana kar. phir is se khoon ka lothrha bana kar. phir is se booti bana kar jis ki banawat kaamil bhi hoti hai aur naaqis bhi taakay tum par ( apni khaalqiyat ) zahir kar dein. aur hum jis ko chahtay hain aik meyaad muqarrar taq pait mein thehraye rakhtay hain phir tum ko bacha bana kar nikaltay hain. phir tum jawani ko pahunchte ho. aur baaz ( qabal az peeri mrjate hain aur baaz Sheikh fali ho jatay aur burhapay ki ) nihayat kharab Umar ki taraf lout’tay jatay hain ke bohat kuch jan-nay ke baad bilkul be ilm ho jatay hain. aur ( ae dekhnay walay ) to daikhta hai ( ke aik waqt mein ) zameen khushk ( pari hoti hai ) phir jab hum is par meen barastee hain to shadaab hojati aur ubharnay lagti hai aur terhan terhan ki baronq cheezein ugati hai
  22,6,un qudraton se zahir hai ke khuda hi ( Qadir mutlaq hai jo ) barhaq hai aur yeh ke woh mardon ko zindah kardaita hai. aur yeh ke woh har cheez par qudrat rakhta hai
  22,7,aur yeh ke qayamat anay wali hai. is mein kuch shak nahi. aur yeh ke khuda sab logon ko jo qabron mein hain jala uthaye ga
  22,8,aur logon mein koi aisa bhi hai jo khuda ( ki shaan ) mein baghair ilm (o danish ) ke aur baghair hadaayat ke aur baghair kitaab roshan ke jhgerta hai
  22,9,( aur taqqabur se ) gardan mourr laita ( hai ) taakay ( logon ko ) khuda ke raste se gumraah kardey. is ke liye duniya mein zillat hai. aur qayamat ke din hum usay azaab ( aatish ) sozaa ka maza chkhayin ge
  22,10,( ae sarkash ) yeh is ( kufar ) ki saza hai jo tairay hathon ne agay bheja hai aur khuda apne bundon par zulm karne wala nahi
  22,11,aur logon mein baaz aisa bhi hai jo kinare par ( khara ho kar ) khuda ki ibadat karta hai. agar is ko koi ( dunyawi ) faida puhanche to is ke sabab mutmaen hojaye aur agar koi aafat parre to munh ke bil lout jaye ( yani phir kafir hojaye ) is ne duniya mein bhi nuqsaan uthaya aur akhirat mein bhi. yahi to nuqsaan Sarih hai
  22,12,yeh khuda ke siwa aisi cheez ko pukaarta hai jo nah usay nuqsaan p_hnchaye aur nah faida day sakay. yahi to parlay darjay ki gumraahi hai
  22,13,aisay shakhs ko pukaarta hai jis ka nuqsaan faida se ziyada qareeb hai. aisa dost bura bhi aur aisa hum sohbat bhi bura
  22,14,jo log imaan laaye aur amal naik karte rahay khuda un ko bahishtoon mein daakhil kere ga jin ke neechay nehrain chal rahen hain. kuch shak nahi ke khuda jo chahta hai karta hai
  22,15,jo shakhs yeh gumaan karta hai ke khuda is ko duniya aur akhirat mein madad nahi day ga to is ko chahiye ke oopar ki taraf ( yani apne ghar ki chhat mein ) aik rassi bandhay phir ( is se apna ) gala ghoont le. phir dekhe ke aaya yeh tadbeer is ke ghusse ko daur kardeti hai
  22,16,aur isi terhan hum ne is quran ko utaara hai ( jis ki tamam ) baatein khuli hui ( hain ) aur yeh ( yaad rakho ) ke khuda jis ko chahta hai Hadayat deta hai
  22,17,jo log momin ( yani musalman ) hain aur jo yahodi hain aur sitara parast aur isaai aur majoosi aur mushriq. khuda un ( sab ) mein qayamat ke din faisla kardey ga. be shak khuda har cheez se bakhabar hai
  22,18,kiya tum ne nahi dekha ke jo ( makhlooq ) asmano mein hai aur jo zameen mein hai aur Sooraj aur chaand setaaray aur pahar aur darakht aur chaar paye aur bohat se ensaan khuda ko sajda karte hain. aur bohat se aisay hain jin par azaab saabit hochuka hai. aur jis shakhs ko khuda zaleel kere is ko izzat dainay wala nahi. be shak khuda jo chahta hai karta hai
  22,19,yeh do ( fareeq ) aik dosray ke dushman apne perwar-digaar ( ke baray ) mein jhagarte hain. to kafir hain un ke liye aag ke kapray qata kiye jayen ge ( aur ) un ke suron par jalta howa pani dala jaye ga
  22,20,is se un ke pait ke andar ki cheezein aur khalin Gul jayen gi
  22,21,aur un ( ke maarny thoknay ) ke liye lohay ke hathoray hon ge
  22,22,jab woh chahain ge ke is ranj ( wa takleef ) ki wajah se dozakh se nikal jayen to phir isi mein lota diye jayen ge. aur ( kaha jaye ga ke ) julne ke azaab ka maza chahkte raho
  22,23,jo log imaan laaye aur amal naik karte rahay khuda un ko bahishtoon mein daakhil kere ga jin ke taley nehrain beh rahen hain. wahan un ko sonay ke kangon pahnaye jayen ge aur moti. aur wahan un ka libaas reshmi hoga
  22,24,aur un ko pakeeza kalaam ki hadaayat ki gayi aur ( khuday-e ) hmid ki raah batayi gayi
  22,25,jo log kafir hain aur ( logon ko ) khuda ke raste se aur masjid mohtaram se jisay hum ne logon ke liye yaksaa ( ibadat gaah ) banaya hai roktay hain. khuwa wahan ke rehne walay hon ya bahar se anay walay. aur jo is mein shararat se kajrawi (o kufar) karna chahay is ko hum dard dainay walay azaab ka maza chkhayin ge .
  22,26,( aur aik waqt tha ) jab hum ne ibrahim ke liye khanah kaaba ko muqarrarkiya ( aur irshad farmaya ) ke mere sath kisi cheez ko shareek nah kejio aur tuwaf karne walon aur qiyam karne walon aur ruku karne walon ( aur ) sajda karne walon ke liye mere ghar ko saaf rakha karo
  22,27,aur logon mein hajj ke liye nida kar do ke tumhari paidal aur dublay dublay oonton par jo daur daraaz rustoon se chalay atay ho ( sawaar ho kar ) chalay ayen
  22,28,taakay apne faiday ke kamon ke liye haazir hon. aur ( qurbani ke ) ayyaam maloom mein chahar payaan maweshi ( ke zibah ke waqt ) jo khuda ne un ko diye hain un par khuda ka naam len. is mein se tum khud bhi khao aur faqeer darmandah ko bhi khilao
  22,29,phir chahiye ke log apna mil kuchail daur karen aur nazren poori karen aur Khana qadeem ( yani beeet allah ) ka tuwaf karen
  22,30,yeh ( hamara hukum hai ) jo shakhs adab ki cheezon ki jo khuda ne muqarrar ki hain Azmat rakhay to yeh perwar-digaar ke nazdeek is ke haq mein behtar hai. aur tumahray liye maweshi halal kardiye gay hain. siwa un ke jo tumhe parh kar sunaye jatay hain to buton ki پلیدی se bachcho aur jhooti baat se ijtinab karo
  22,31,sirf aik khuda ke ho kar is ke sath shareek nah tehra kar. aur jo shakhs ( kisi ko ) khuda ke sath shareek muqarrar kere to woh goya aisa hai jaisay aasman se gir parre phir is ko parinday uchak le jayen ya howa kisi daur jagah urra kar pheink day
  22,32,( yeh hamara hukum hai ) aur jo shakhs adab ki cheezon ki jo khuda ne muqarrar ki hain Azmat rakhay to yeh ( feal ) dilon ki parhaiz gari mein se hai
  22,33,un mein aik waqt muqarrar taq tumahray liye faiday hain phir un ko Khana qadeem ( yani beeet allah ) taq pahunchana ( aur zibah hona ) hai
  22,34,aur hum ne har aُmt ke liye qurbani ka tareeq muqarrar kardiya hai taakay jo maweshi charpaye khuda ne un ko diye hain ( un ke zibah karne ke waqt ) un par khuda ka naam len. so tumhara mabood aik hi hai to isi ke farmanbardar hojao. aur aajzi karne walon ko khushkhabri suna do
  22,35,yeh woh log hain ke jab khuda ka naam liya jata hai to un ke dil dar jatay hain aur jab un par museebat padtee hai to sabr karte hain aur namaz aadaab se parhte hain aur jo ( maal ) hum ne un ko ataa farmaya hai ( is mein se ) ( naik kamon mein ) kharch karte hain
  22,36,aur qurbani ke oonton ko bhi hum ne tumahray liye Shaer khuda muqarrarkiya hai. un mein tumahray liye faiday hain. to ( qurbani karne ke waqt ) qitaar bandh kar un par khuda ka naam lau. jab pehlu ke bil gir parrin to un mein se khao aur Qanaat se baith rehne walon aur sawal karne walon ko bhi khilao. is terhan hum ne un ko tumahray zairay farman kardiya hai taakay tum shukar karo
  22,37,khuda taq nah unn ka gosht pohanchana hai aur nah khoon. balkay is taq tumhari parhaiz gari pahunchti hai. isi terhan khuda ne un ko tumhara maskhar kar diya hai taakay is baat ke badlay ke is ne tum ko hadaayat bakhsh hai usay buzurgi se yaad karo. aur ( ae paighambar ) naiko karon ko khushkhabri suna do
  22,38,khuda to mominon se un ke dushmanon ko htata rehta hai. be shak khuda kisi khayanat karne walay aur kufran Nemat karne walay ko dost nahi rakhta .
  22,39,jin musalmanoon se ( khuwa makhuwa ) larai ki jati hai un ko ijazat hai ( ke woh bhi lrhin ) kyunkay un par zulm ho raha hai. aur khuda ( un ki madad kere ga woh ) yaqeenan un ki madad par Qadir hai
  22,40,yeh woh log hain ke apne gharon se na-haq nikaal diye gay ( unhon ne kuch qasoor nahikiya ) haan yeh kehte hain ke hamara perwar-digaar khuda hai. aur agar khuda logon ko aik dosray se nah htata rehta to ( rahibon ke ) sawamay aur ( esaion ke ) girgay aur ( yahudion ke ) ibadat khanaay aur ( musalmanoon ki ) msjdin jin mein khuda ka bohat sa zikarkiya jata hai weraan hochuki hoten. aur jo shakhs khuda ki madad karta hai khuda is ki zaroor madad karta hai. be shak khuda tawana aur ghalib hai
  22,41,yeh woh log hain ke agar hum un ko malik mein dustarus den to namaz parheen aur zakaat ada karen aur naik kaam karne ka hukum den aur buray kamon se mana karen aur sab kamon ka injaam khuda hi ke ikhtiyar mein hai
  22,42,aur agar yeh log tum ko jutlatay hain un se pehlay Nooh ki qoum aur Aad وﺛمود bhi ( apne payghambaroon ko ) jhutla chuke hain
  22,43,aur qoum ibrahim aur qoum Loot bhi
  22,44,aur Mudin ke rehne walay bhi. aur moose bhi to ghutlaye ja chukay hain lekin mein kafiroon ko mohlat deta raha phir un ko pakar liya. to ( dekh lau ) ke mera azaab kaisa ( sakht ) tha
  22,45,aur bohat si bastiyan hain ke hum ne un ko tabah kar dala ke woh nafarman theen. so woh apni chaton par giri pari hain. aur ( bohat se ) kunwein be car aur ( bohat se ) mehal weraan parre hain
  22,46,kiya un logon ne malik mein sair nahi ki taakay un ke dil ( aisay ) hotay ke un se samajh satke. aur kaan ( aisay ) hotay ke un se sun satke. baat yeh hai ke ankhen andhi nahi hoten balkay dil jo seenon mein hain ( woh ) andhay hotay hain
  22,47,aur ( yeh log ) tum se azaab ke liye jaldi kar rahay hain aur khuda apna wada hargiz khilaaf nahi kere ga. aur be shak tumahray perwar-digaar ke nazdeek aik roz tumahray hisaab ke ro se hazaar baras ke barabar hai
  22,48,aur bohat si bastiyan hain ke mein un ko mohlat deta raha aur woh nafarman theen. phir mein ne un ko pakar liya. aur meri taraf hi lout kar aana hai
  22,49,( ae paighambar ) keh do ke logo! mein tum ko khullam khula nasiyaat karne wala hon
  22,50,to jo log imaan laaye aur naik kaam kiye un ke liye bakhshish aur aabaroo ki rozi hai
  22,51,"aur jin logon ne hamari ayaton mein ( apne zeam baatil mein ) hamein aajiz karne ke liye sae ki, woh ahal dozakh hain"
  22,52,aur hum ne tum se pehlay koi rasool aur nabi nahi bheja magar ( is ka yeh haal tha ke ) jab woh koi arzoo karta tha to shetan is ki arzoo mein ( waswasa ) daal deta tha. to jo ( waswasa ) shetan dalta hai khuda is ko daur kardaita hai. phir khuda apni ayaton ko mazboot kardaita hai. aur khuda ilm wala aur hikmat wala hai
  22,53,gharz ( is se ) yeh hai ke jo ( waswasa ) shetan dalta hai is ko un logon ke liye jin ke dilon mein bemari hai aur jin ke dil sakht hain zareya azmaish thehraye. be shak zalim parlay darjay ki mukhalfat mein hain
  22,54,aur yeh bhi gharz hai ke jin logon ko ilm ataa howa hai woh jaan len ke woh ( yani wahi ) tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se haq hai to woh is par imaan layein aur un ke dil khuda ke agay aajzi karen. aur jo log imaan laaye hain khuda un ko seedhay raste ki taraf hadaayat karta hai
  22,55,aur kafir log hamesha is se shak mein rahen ge yahan taq ke qayamat un par nagahan aajay ya aik namubarak din ka azaab un par waqay ho
  22,56,is roz badshahi khuda hi ki hogi. aur un mein faisla kardey ga to jo log imaan laaye aur amal naik karte rahay woh Nemat ke baghoon mein hon ge
  22,57,aur jo kafir hue aur hamari ayaton ko jutlatay rahay un ke liye zaleel karne wala azaab hoga
  22,58,aur jin logon ne khuda ki raah mein hijrat ki phir maaray gay ya mar gay. un ko khuda achi rozi day ga. aur be shak khuda sab se behtar rizaq dainay wala hai
  22,59,woh un ko aisay maqam mein daakhil kere ga jisay woh pasand karen ge. aur khuda to jan-nay wala ( aur ) Burdbar hai
  22,60,yeh ( baat khuda ke haan thehr chuki hai ) aur jo shakhs ( kisi ko ) itni hi aeza day jitni aeza is ko di gayi phir is shakhs par zayad-ti ki jaye to khuda is ki madad kere ga. be shak khuda maaf karne wala aur bakhsnay wala hai
  22,61,yeh is liye ke khuda raat ko din mein daakhil kardaita hai aur din ko raat mein daakhil karta hai. aur khuda to suneney wala dekhnay wala hai
  22,62,yeh is liye ke khuda hi barhaq hai aur jis cheez ko ( kafir ) khuda ke siwa pkarte hain woh baatil hai aur is liye khuda Rafi al shan aur bara hai
  22,63,kiya tum nahi dekhte ke khuda aasman se meen barsata hai to zameen sirsabz hojati hai. be shak khuda bareek bain aur khabardaar hai
  22,64,jo kuch asmano mein hai aur jo kuch zameen mein hai isi ka hai. aur be shak khuda be niaz aur qabil sataish hai .
  22,65,kiya tum nahi dekhte ke jitni cheezein zameen mein hain ( sab ) khuda ne tumahray zeray farman kar rakhi hain aur kashtiyan ( bhi ) jo isi ke hukum se darya mein chalti hain. aur woh aasman ko thaamay rehta hai ke zameen par ( nah ) gur parre magar is ke hukum se. be shak khuda logon par nihayat shafqat karne wala meharban hai
  22,66,aur wohi to hai jis ne tum ko hayaat bakhsh. phir tum ko maarta hai. phir tumhe zindah bhi kere ga. aur ensaan to bara na shukar hai
  22,67,hum ne har aik aُmt ke liye aik Shariat muqarrar kar di hai jis par woh chaltay hain to yeh log tum se is amar mein jhagra nah karen aur tum ( logon ko ) apne perwar-digaar ki taraf bulatay raho. be shak tum seedhay raste par ho
  22,68,aur agar yeh tum se jhagra karen to keh do ke jo amal tum karte ho khuda un se khoob waaqif hai
  22,69,jin baton mein tum ikhtilaaf karte ho khuda tum mein qayamat ke roz un ka faisla kardey ga
  22,70,kiya tum nahi jantay ke jo kuch aasman aur zameen mein hai khuda is ko jaanta hai. yeh ( sab kuch ) kitaab mein ( likha howa ) hai. be shak yeh sab khuda ko aasaan hai
  22,71,aur ( yeh log ) khuda ke siwa aisi cheezon ki ibadat karte hain jin ki is ne koi sanad nazil nahi farmai aur nah un ke paas is ki koi Daleel hai. aur zaalmon ka koi bhi madadgaar nahi hoga
  22,72,aur jab un ko hamari ayatain parh kar sunai jati to ( un ki shakal baggar jati hai aur ) tum un ke cheharon mein saaf tor par na khushi ( ke assaar ) dekhte ho. qareeb hotay hain ke jo log un ko hamari ayatain parh kar sunaate hain un par hamla kar dein. keh do ke mein tum ko is se bhi buri cheez batau? woh dozakh ki aag hai. jis ka khuda ne kafiroon se wadakiya hai. aur woh bura thikana hai
  22,73,logo! aik misaal bayan ki jati hai usay ghhor se suno. ke jin logon ko tum khuda ke siwa pkarte ho woh aik makhi bhi nahi bana satke agarchay is ke liye sab mujtma ho jaien. aur agar un se makhi koi cheez le jaye to usay is se churra nahi satke. taalib aur matloob ( yani abid aur mabood dono ) gay guzray hain
  22,74,un logon ne khuda ki qader jaisi karni chahiye thi nahi ki. kuch shak nahi ke khuda zabardast aur ghalib hai
  22,75,khuda firshton mein se pegham pohanchanay walay munhtakhib karleta hai aur insanon mein se bhi. be shak khuda suneney wala ( aur ) dekhnay wala hai
  22,76,jo un ke agay hai aur jin un ke peechay hai woh is se waaqif hai. aur sab kamon ka rujoo khuda hi ki taraf hai
  22,77,momino! ruku karte aur sjday karte aur apne perwar-digaar ki ibadat karte raho aur naik kaam karo taakay Falah pao
  22,78,aur khuda ( ki raah ) mein jehaad karo jaissa jehaad karne ka haq hai. is ne tum ko bargzidakiya hai aur tum par deen ki ( kisi baat ) mein tangi nahi ki. ( aur tumahray liye ) tumahray baap ibrahim ka deen ( pasandkiya ) usi ne pehlay ( yani pehli kitabon mein ) tumhara naam musalman rakha tha aur is kitaab mein bhi ( wohi naam rakha hai to jehaad karo ) taakay paighambar tumahray baray mein Shahid hon. aur tum logon ke muqablay mein Shahid aur namaz parho aur zakaat do aur khuda ke deen ki ( rassi ko ) pakdae raho. wohi tumhara dost hai. aur khoob dost aur khoob madadgaar hai
